snippet.title: Big Buck Hunter Reloaded Official Trailer
snippet.description:
https://arcadeheroes.com - Official trailer provided to us by Raw Thrills, showing the biggest update to the Big Buck Hunter franchise since the series was completely revamped in 2012 with Big Buck HD. 

Coming to bars and arcades in 2020
